# Quick Start Template - Simple Feature Requirements
# Just fill in the blanks below!

Feature: [What feature are you building?]
  As a [who is the user?]
  I want to [what do they want to do?]
  So that [why do they want to do it?]

  Scenario: [Happy path - describe the main success case]
    Given [what's the starting situation?]
    When [what action does the user take?]
    Then [what should happen?]

  Scenario: [Error case - what could go wrong?]
    Given [what's the error situation?]
    When [what triggers the error?]
    Then [how should the system respond?]


